      match $x isa <attr>; $x >= <pivot>;
      sort $x asc;
      """
    Then order of answer concepts is
      | x                     |
      | attr:<attr>:<pivot>   |
      | attr:<attr>:<greater> |

    # descending
    When get answers of typeql read query
      """
      match $x isa <attr>; $x < <pivot>;
      sort $x desc;
      """
    Then order of answer concepts is
      | x                    |
      | attr:<attr>:<lesser> |

    When get answers of typeql read query
      """
      match $x isa <attr>; $x <= <pivot>;
      sort $x desc;
      """
    Then order of answer concepts is
      | x                    |
      | attr:<attr>:<pivot>  |
      | attr:<attr>:<lesser> |

    When get answers of typeql read query
      """
      match $x isa <attr>; $x > <pivot>;
      sort $x desc;
      """
    Then order of answer concepts is
      | x                     |
